**Category [:en]Goods and Services** {GD}

**Notice Type [:en]Request for Proposal** {Demande de propositions}

**Procurement Method [:en]Competitive - Open bidding** {Concurrentielle - Invitation ouverte à soumissionner}

**Procurement Category**: The Department of National Defence invites bidders to submit proposals for the procurement of various thermostats.

**Description [:en]**

The Department of National Defence requires the following thermostats:

* Item 1, GSIN: 6685, NSN: 20-A0F3173 (80 units) to be delivered to CFB Esquimalt.
* Item 2, GSIN: 6685, NSN: 20-A0F3173 (80 units) to be delivered to CFB Halifax.
* Item 3, GSIN: 6685, NSN: 20-A0F3174 (80 units) to be delivered to CFB Esquimalt.
* Item 4, GSIN: 6685, NSN: 20-A0F3174 (80 units) to be delivered to CFB Halifax.

Bidders proposing an equivalent or substitute product must indicate the brand name, model and/or part number and the NCAGE they are offering. Canadian content is preferred (CFTA) and bidders must submit prices in Canadian dollars.

